ActionNetwork,org,is,an,online,organizing,resource,that,groups,can,use,to,promote,campaigns,and,petition,for,progressive,causes,Users,can,create,petitions,to,collect,signatures,create,forms,to,collect,information,schedule,events,create,groups,assemble,fundraisers,and,more,The,Action,Network,API,allows,community,organizers,to,access,their,core,API,in,order,to,send,GET,POST,and,PUT,requests,to,return,lists,of,supporters,petition,signers,add,people,to,the,email,list,post,new,fundraising,pages,unsubscribe,people,from,the,list,and,more